high_descs: Walk forward across the room and turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk around the table to face the counter with tomato and apple on it on the far side of the room.
Cut the apple into three pieces.
Turn left, walk forward to the fridge and turn right to face it.
Place the knife on the top shelf in the fridge.
Turn right and walk forward and then turn left to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the apple on the counter.
Turn right and walk over to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left, walk forward to the fridge and turn right to face it.
Place the piece of apple in the freezer.
anns.task_desc: To cut an apple as well as place a piece in the freezer.

high_descs: Go forward, hang a left and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the big knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge, hang a right, go forward to the counter with the paper towels on it that is on the left.
Cut the apple that is on the counter behind the paper towels.
Turn around, go to the right to the fridge that will be on the right.
Open the fridge, put the knife inside, close the fridge.
Go to the right, go to the counter where the apple is on the left.
Pick up a piece of the apple.
Turn around, then turn to the left, go forward to the microwave that is on the left.
Put the apple in the microwave and set it to cook, remove the apple when it is done cooking.
Turn around, turn to the right and go forward to the fridge that is on the right.
Open the freezer, put the apple in the freezer and close the freezer.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked apple in the freezer.

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around, cross the room, face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Go to the left to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf of the bottom part of the fridge.
Turn right, walk to the center of the counter on the left.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Walk to the right to the microwave.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave for a few seconds, take the apple slice back out.
Walk to left to the fridge.
Put the apple slice in the top part of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the warm apple slice in the fridge.
